      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>Hm, but can't any app on the device access it? without camera permission? and it seems like a webpage can then grab frames and do anything with them too.</p>

<p>You can use the source code and libraries, sure. See <a href="https://github.com/zxing/zxing/wiki/License-Questions">https://github.com/zxing/zxing/wiki/License-Questions</a> for notes but it's just AL2 licensed. Here there is no issue of cloning the UI. I would not use the project name or icon if you please, just to make it clear it is a third-party project.</p>
